  title `The Illegal Migrants (Determination by Tribunals) Act, 1983`
  actNumber (39)
  enactmentDate 1983-12-25
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1766`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `अवैध प्रवासी (अधिकरणों द्वारा अवधारण) अधिनियम, 1983`
  actYear (1983)
  ministry `Ministry of Home Affairs`
  department `Department of Internal Security`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the establishment of Tribunals for the determination, in a fair manner, of the question whether a person is an illegal migrant to enable the Central Government to expel illegal migrants from India and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
